data.description: This rarely used, elegant condo located in the highly-sought-after Tangier Sound Condominium, comes turnkey and beautifully-fully-furnished, with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Nicely-decorated throughout, and freshly painted, the flat is detailed with ceramic tile and plush carpet in the bedrooms, and offers ample space, including a primary suite with a separate soaking tub and shower, with access to the large balcony that overlooks the Tangier Sound/Chesapeake Bay. These 3rd-floor views aren’t limited to the main bedroom (which comes complete with crown molding and a tray ceiling), as you’ll also find the living room boasts its own brilliant vistas. This spacious-area features a fireplace and spills out to the scenic balcony, ideal for enjoying the impeccable sunsets, your morning coffee or your beverage of choice. This luxurious condo has an open floor-plan with a roomy kitchen, complete with granite countertops, an island, and barstools, perfect for a late-morning brunch.  An easy, 20-minute walk brings you into downtown Crisfield, famous for its seafood and home to the National Hard Crab Derby. And for dessert, the ferry to Smith Island, renowned for its delicious cake, is a short-ride away. Your new home also comes with a deeded boat slip!  Don’t miss your chance at this lovely condo, in the tranquil setting of Crisfield, where you only need your personal belongings to feel right at home! Professional Photos to Follow!
